{"tid":2164045,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"世道人生：將「兩害」轉化為「兩利」（李怡）","createTime":"2020-08-19T04:08:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-19T08:32:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"75f7d8f67ca4226be6a061fa2e8f71b682020f30","tid":2164045,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T04:08:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200819/ZAPFKJ2ARRGUXBKY64NOWYLY2E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200819%2FZAPFKJ2ARRGUXBKY64NOWYLY2E%2F&d=MYvC0VRZm9a3oqKPvUvInPolgVFqTZkzW3om5iGclzM%3D&h=7ced82cc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200819%2FZAPFKJ2ARRGUXBKY64NOWYLY2E%2F&h=6f8a4236\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200819/ZAPFKJ2ARRGUXBKY64NOWYLY2E/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n世道人生：將「兩害」轉化為「兩利」（李怡）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/1-V23G8IY8qXtyXnMb44jRq9JDU=/2682x1674/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MPRV6I3GXRBCTI6GGDW6DDOA5Q.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F1-V23G8IY8qXtyXnMb44jRq9JDU%3D%2F2682x1674%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMPRV6I3GXRBCTI6GGDW6DDOA5Q.gif&h=80e56bf2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n按照《基本法》，第六屆立法會議員的四年任期已告結束，因此，人大常委決定原有議員延任「不少於一年」，就不是原來選民所賦予四年任期的「民命」，而是非《基本法》所定的「中央」的「委任」。如果原有議員接受委任，就是接受一種違反《基本法》定下立法會議員產生的方式；如果不接受，那也不是「總辭」，而是表明不接受沒有香港民意授權的委任而已。<br />\n<br />\n民主派議員接受與否，成為兩難選擇。他們多次開會尋求共識，希望延續去年反送中以來的「齊上齊落」，但無法取得一致。前日傳出大部份主「留」，也有主「留」派提出「兩害取其輕」的一些理據，但主「去」派也提出理據，並建議通過公投或民調決定。<br />\n<br />\n主「留」的民主黨主席胡志偉指，如果市民不滿意，在2021年的選舉中即使將選票投給本土派、新興力量都無問題。從早前民主派初選結果和近日網上取向來看，答案可能不是「如果」，而是「必然」。<br />\n<br />\n確實是兩害。「留」，有港共和建制派說他們「重新做人」這類死亡祝福，明年選舉一定失利；更何況一旦接受了委任，「不少於一年」就可以是兩年、三年持續委任下去。「去」，則少了議會抗爭手段，儘管已經連關鍵少數都不具備，但還有拖延手段，又少了受媒體關注的議員身份，不能把議會爭議帶入社會，當然更少了大筆收入。<br />\n<br />\n昨天曾志豪說：「這是一個無論去或留，泛民都會遍體鱗傷的政治陰謀。」恐怕正是如此。沒有「取其輕」的「害」，都是要「害」。<br />\n<br />\n要害在哪裏？就在於製造民主派的分裂。過去議會泛民與本土派、抗爭派爭拗不止，而去年反送中運動就把不同取向的民主派聯結起來，兄弟各自爬山、不割席、不篤灰，年輕抗爭派大力動員市民參加和理非遊行，抗爭者的激烈行動也得到和理非泛民支持。延續到區議會選舉和民主派初選，聯手局面似已形成。這是中港共最不想見到的局面。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n這是轉危為機、將「兩害」轉化「兩利」的一個辦法。唯一的損失是少了大筆資源。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/mrleeyee\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmrleeyee&d=MYvC0VRZm9a3oqKPvUvInPolgVFqTZkzW3om5iGclzM%3D&h=c4e83e6e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.facebook.com/mrleeyee</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n李怡"},{"pid":"0be589e365b3fa5aefe263dc887e63bd48fd4c98","tid":2164045,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T04:11:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d890427c9f9c6ceaba83b898f9d162ad95d7c30","tid":2164045,"uid":8948,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T04:21:35.000Z","msg":"DQ四子留任就係拎返主導權嘅其中一個手段<br />\n唔可以永遠順住港共定嘅路線陪佢玩<br />\n<br />\n因為佢地係最清楚「民主」嘅弱點，就係下決定唔會夠果斷，因為揹住民意包袱<br />\n<br />\n只要港共逼所有「民主派」要係短時間內做多個重要決定，就必然可以分化到佢地嘅團結，因為民主必然要求討論分析<br />\n<br />\n然後仲要考慮唔留任嘅「前議員」佢地可以做乜，我覺得就係籌備選舉，改善 民間公投系統，搞選民登記，令「民主派」以後下決定可以有一個更高效率嘅制度"},{"pid":"142a67c91c7f667827ed981e604b94baaf49ab15","tid":2164045,"uid":47042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T04:56:49.000Z","msg":"初頭覺得只留四個好膠<br />\n<br />\n但慢慢發展落去，似係出路"},{"pid":"2e3b03dd236f729cf4fedd8ac318d424d45365e5","tid":2164045,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T05:21:37.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4c1c684468faf15d64971a2c7577dc94a740f92","tid":2164045,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T05:23:53.000Z","msg":"Post 錯 link<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200819/CU6RFFEU6JCUVM4QTXQL3WL75A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200819%2FCU6RFFEU6JCUVM4QTXQL3WL75A%2F&d=MYvC0VRZm9a3oqKPvUvInPolgVFqTZkzW3om5iGclzM%3D&h=387c4eea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200819%2FCU6RFFEU6JCUVM4QTXQL3WL75A%2F&h=31a9e07e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200819/CU6RFFEU6JCUVM4QTXQL3WL75A/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/1-V23G8IY8qXtyXnMb44jRq9JDU=/2682x1674/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MPRV6I3GXRBCTI6GGDW6DDOA5Q.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F1-V23G8IY8qXtyXnMb44jRq9JDU%3D%2F2682x1674%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMPRV6I3GXRBCTI6GGDW6DDOA5Q.gif&h=80e56bf2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c83b530b1c53ad6376c9f547b5b19ef87fc64a55","tid":2164045,"uid":147895,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T05:32:20.000Z","msg":"我要強調一下，反送中係泛民自己痴埋黎張席到，本土派好心先侵埋佢玩，而家泛民係到拖後腳，出賣香港人，唔洗旨意抗爭者再當泛民係自己人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"099b4e5d3b700d5ac28adc158e02612029a446fe","tid":2164045,"uid":281376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"75f7d8f67ca4226be6a061fa2e8f71b682020f30","tid":2164045,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T04:08:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200819/ZAPFKJ2ARRGUXBKY64NOWYLY2E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Floc